short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Extension that allows you to search books from the Forsyth County Library of books with ease!

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension is your one-stop-shop for all things Forsyth County Library! With it, you can now search for books without ever leaving your browser, among a number of other cool features. Ever wanted a page that connected the Forsyth County Library offerings with easy and efficient access to Goodreads? Here it is! Ever wished you could receive immediate data regarding popularity trends and long-term relevancy about the book you are searching for? It, and much more, has arrived!
